text: "One Tree Hill" is a 1988 song by Irish rock group U2 and is the fourth single from their fifth studio album The Joshua Tree. It went to number 1 in New Zealand and was released only in New Zealand and Australia. In the United States their fourth single was In God's Country. ==Track listing== == References == Category:1988 songs Category:Rock songs Category:U2 songs
